description: Number of distinct 5th powers mod n.
comments: This sequence is multiplicative. - Leon P Smith, Apr 16 2005
links: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
prog: (PARI) a(n)=my(f=factor(n)); prod(i=1, #f[, 1], my(k=f[i, 1]^f[i, 2]); #vecsort(vector(k, i, i^5%k), , 8)) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Sep 05 2013

author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Feb 05 2000
